    Page: 717-718
  Source:
    Title: Yoga-Vasishtha
Tags:
  - Discernment-Truth=Spiritual Drowning
  - Union-Identity=Mysterium Magnum=Non-Duality
---
Go and plunge yourself into the calm sea of spiritual solitude, and wash your
soul in the nectar of ambrosial meditation. Dive and dive deep in the depth of
Unity, and fly from the salt waves of duality and the brackish water of
diversity.
